normalization: min-max normalization of raw_mu within TRAIN period

metadata.ground_truth_description: raw_mu = average daily return over next 21 days
metadata.raw_total_sigma_description: raw_total_sigma = cumulative volatility over 21 days (sigma * sqrt(21))
metadata.rho_description: rho = (raw_mu - min_raw_mu) / (max_raw_mu - min_raw_mu) [computed within TRAIN period]
